[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0975","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0975.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0654","title":"Microsoft Windows NT OS/2 与 POSIX 子系统安全漏洞","description":"Windows NT 默认启用的 OS/2 和 POSIX 子系统存在安全绕过漏洞。这两个子系统拥有独立的权限模型和 API 接口，当被启用时，本地攻击者可以利用子系统间的安全策略差异，通过运行 OS/2 或 POSIX 格式的可执行程序绕过 Windows NT 的原生安全机制，导致权限提升或安全策略绕过。该漏洞危害等级严重（CVSS 10.0），影响所有启用 OS/2 或 POSIX 子系统的 Windows NT 版本。建议禁用不必要的子系统以降低风险。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0654"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:47.320","remediation":"如无需 OS/2 兼容支持，在注册表 `HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Session Manager\\SubSystems` 中删除 `Os2` 和 `Posix` 子系统的注册值，或将其设为 `%systemroot%\\system32\\os2srv.exe` 为空，然后重启系统使配置生效。如仅需其一，保留对应项、删除另一项即可，无需卸载整个系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0654"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0975.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0974","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0974.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0653","title":"Sun NIS+ 服务远程未授权访问漏洞","description":"NIS+（Network Information Service Plus）是 Sun Microsystems 开发的网络目录服务，用于集中管理用户账户、主机名和密码等敏感信息。该漏洞源于目标系统上运行的 NIS+ 服务未配置适当的访问控制机制，远程攻击者无需任何身份认证即可通过网络向 NIS+ 服务发起查询请求，获取系统中的密码哈希、网络配置和用户信息等敏感数据，严重时可导致攻击者完全控制目标系统。CVSS v2 评分为 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0653"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:47.190","remediation":"立即停止并禁用 NIS+ 相关服务（如 rpc.nisd），在防火墙上阻止对 RPC 端口映射服务 (TCP/UDP 111) 和 NIS+ 相关端口的入站访问。如业务需要，建议迁移至 LDAP/Kerberos 作为替代方案，并对 NIS+ 服务实施严格的主机访问控制列表 (hosts.allow/hosts.deny)。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0653"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0974.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0973","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0973.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0652","title":"多款数据库服务暴露导致的信息泄露风险配置","description":"CVE-1999-0652 已被撤销（REJECT），原内容描述的是数据库服务（如 SQL Server、Oracle、MySQL 等）直接暴露在网络上的不安全配置问题。攻击者通过网络扫描可发现开放数据库端口，在未授权情况下尝试弱口令或默认凭证登录，进而窃取、篡改或删除敏感数据。此类风险属于安全配置缺陷而非软件漏洞，故该编号已被弃用，相关配置建议已纳入通用配置枚举（CCE）。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0652"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.253","remediation":"不应将数据库服务直接暴露在公网，应将数据库绑定到 127.0.0.1 或内网 IP，通过防火墙限制 1433（SQL Server）、1521（Oracle）、3306（MySQL）等端口的入站流量，仅允许受信任的应用服务器 IP 访问。同时启用强身份认证、禁用默认账户，并定期更新数据库补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0973.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0971","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0971.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0651","title":"Unix R系列服务远程未授权访问漏洞","description":"rsh/rlogin 服务默认不加密传输所有数据，包括用户凭据和命令内容，且其基于 IP 地址的信任认证机制极易被伪造。攻击者可通过网络嗅探截获明文凭据，或通过 IP 欺骗绕过信任认证直接远程登录目标主机执行任意命令。该问题影响所有运行 rsh/rlogin 服务的 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。修复方法为禁用 rsh/rlogin 服务，改用 SSH 等加密协议。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0651"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:47.017","remediation":"禁用 rsh/rlogin 服务：在 inetd/xinetd 配置中注释或删除 shell/login 服务条目，执行 `systemctl disable rsh.socket rlogin.socket`（systemd 系统）或重启 inetd 服务。使用 SSH 替代 rsh/rlogin 进行远程管理，在防火墙上阻断端口 513/tcp（rlogin）和 514/tcp（rsh）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2995"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0971.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0969","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0969.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0650","title":"Unix Netstat 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"netstat 服务（TCP 端口 15）默认开放且未限制访问来源，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统的 netstat 服务发送查询请求，获取当前网络连接状态、路由表、网络接口及协议统计信息。该服务的信息泄露特性使攻击者能够收集内网拓扑结构、活跃连接和服务部署情况，为后续网络嗅探、中间人攻击或针对性渗透提供情报支撑。受影响系统包括运行 netstat 服务的各类 Unix/Linux 发行版。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0650"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.887","remediation":"关闭系统上不必要的 netstat 服务，在 inetd.conf 中注释或删除 netstat 行后重启 inetd 进程；对外部网络在防火墙层面阻断对 netstat 端口（默认 15/tcp）的访问；若需保留本地使用，可移除 setuid 权限并将 netstat 的访问限制为仅 root 用户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/72"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0969.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0968","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0968.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0649","title":"FSP 文件传输服务暴露漏洞","description":"FSP（File Service Protocol）服务运行在目标主机上，该协议未对文件传输提供认证或加密机制。攻击者可通过网络远程访问该服务，可能导致未授权文件读取、写入或信息泄露。该问题属于安全配置缺陷，而非软件漏洞，通常建议在不必要时禁用该服务或通过防火墙限制其访问。CCE（Common Configuration Enumeration）更适用于此类配置问题分类。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0649"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.207","remediation":"建议关闭 FSP 服务（File Service Protocol），或通过防火墙限制仅允许受信 IP 访问端口 21/TCP。若业务需要文件传输功能，应替换为 SFTP 或 SCP 等加密协议，避免使用明文传输的 FSP 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0968.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0967","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0967.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0648","title":"通用 X.25 服务运行配置问题（此编号已废弃，不构成安全漏洞）","description":"tags.<value>CVE-1999-0648 候选编号已被驳回，原因为该条目描述的是\"X25 服务正在运行\"这一系统配置状态，并非直接引入安全漏洞的缺陷类型。此类配置类问题更适合收录于通用配置枚举（CCE）体系。该候选编号不应被用于安全漏洞追踪，其 CVSS 评分为 0，不具备实际可利用的攻击条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0648"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.170","remediation":"如非必要，建议在系统配置中禁用 X.25 服务（如 Solaris 中停止 x25 相关 daemon，Linux 中移除或封锁 x25 内核模块），或在网络边界防火墙封禁 TCP 端口 2000/2001 以限制外部访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0648.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0648","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0648.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0648.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0648.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0967.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0966","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0966.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0647","title":"UNIX bootparamd 服务运行配置问题","description":"bootparamd（引导参数服务）是一种基于 RPC 的传统网络服务，用于向无盘客户端提供引导参数。该服务运行于系统中时，可能被远程攻击者利用来探测网络配置与主机信息，造成信息泄露。由于其本身不直接引入安全漏洞，更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）进行管理。建议在非必要环境中禁用该服务以减少攻击面。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0647"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.137","remediation":"建议在服务器上禁用 bootparamd 服务，该服务用于无盘工作站启动，在现代网络中已无必要且可能泄露系统信息。执行 `killall bootparamd` 并禁止随系统启动（删除或注释相关 inetd 条目）。若确实需要，应在防火墙中限制 RPC 端口 (111/udp) 仅允许受信任子网访问，或配置 hosts.allow/hosts.deny 进行访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0647.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0647","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0647.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0647.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000468.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0647.json","https://github.com/aboutcode-org/aboutcode-mirror-euvd/blob/1b758e4b71978ff973a6df1bc69fc70b932735fb/advisories/2000/02/EUVD-1999-0630.json","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0966.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0965","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0965.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0646","title":"LDAP 服务配置暴露风险","description":"CVE-1999-0646 已被撤销（REJECTED），不再作为安全漏洞使用。该候选编号的原始描述为 LDAP 服务正在运行，仅涉及 LDAP 协议服务的配置暴露情况，并非直接的安全漏洞，不满足 CVE 漏洞收录标准。NVD 官方说明指出该条目更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系进行管理，因此该编号已被废弃。此条目不涉及任何可利用的安全缺陷，不存在攻击条件或利用方式。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0646"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.103","remediation":"如非业务必需，建议禁用 LDAP 匿名绑定，配置 LDAPS（LDAP over SSL/TLS）代替明文 LDAP（端口 389），并在防火墙层面限制只有信任网络可访问 LDAP 端口（389/636）。同时启用访问控制列表（ACL）和账户密码策略，防止信息泄露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0646.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0646","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0646.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0646.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0646.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0965.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0964","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0964.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0645","title":"IRC 服务运行信息泄露漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0645 已被拒绝使用，原分配描述为\"IRC 服务正在运行\"，该条目实质描述的是系统中 IRC 服务处于启用状态的配置信息，而非本身存在安全漏洞。由于此类配置枚举更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系，NVD 已将其标记为 REJECT 状态。系统管理员应关注 IRC 服务是否确实需要运行，若无需使用建议关闭以减小攻击面。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0645"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.070","remediation":"在服务器上禁用不必要的 IRC 服务。Linux 系统执行 systemctl disable ircd 并停止对应服务；Windows 系统通过 services.msc 将 IRC 相关服务设为禁用。在边界防火墙上封禁 IRC 默认端口 6660-6669/TCP 的出站流量，防止内网主机外连 IRC 服务器。定期使用端口扫描确认 6660-6669 端口无对外开放。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0645.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0645","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0645.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0645.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0645.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0964.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0960","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0960.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0642","title":"Multiple Vendors POP Service 未授权访问漏洞","description":"该漏洞条目原描述为目标系统运行了 POP（Post Office Protocol）邮件服务，该服务默认监听 TCP 110 端口。运行 POP 服务本身并不构成直接安全漏洞，但在配置不当（如未启用加密、使用弱口令认证、暴露于公网）的情况下，远程攻击者可能通过暴力破解或会话劫持等方式获取邮件内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该条目已被 CVE 官方驳回，认为其属于通用配置枚举（CCE）范畴而非安全漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0642"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.973","remediation":"如非业务必需，建议在服务器上禁用 POP3 服务（如 CentOS: `systemctl disable dovecot`；Ubuntu: `systemctl disable pop3`）；如确需使用，限制仅允许加密连接（启用 TLS/SSL，设置 `ssl = required`），并在防火墙层面限制仅允许受信 IP 访问 TCP 端口 110。同时建议使用 IMAPS（端口 993）替代明文 POP3。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0642.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0642","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0642.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0642.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0642.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0960.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0958","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0958.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0641","title":"Multiple Unix UUCP 服务远程安全漏洞","description":"UUCP（Unix-to-Unix Copy Protocol）服务默认在 TCP 端口 540 上运行，该服务设计上缺乏充分的身份认证机制，远程攻击者可在无需认证的情况下通过 UUCP 协议与目标系统建立连接，执行文件传输、远程命令执行等操作，导致系统被未授权访问。该问题影响早期运行 UUCP 服务的多种 Unix 系统，攻击者利用此服务可窃取敏感文件或控制系统，危害严重。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0641"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.627","remediation":"立即停止并禁用 UUCP 服务（uucp/uucico），执行 `systemctl stop uucp && systemctl disable uucp`（或对应 init 脚本 `service uucp stop && chkconfig uucp off`）。如业务必须使用，应配置 TCP Wrapper（/etc/hosts.allow 和 /etc/hosts.deny）限制可信来源 IP，并在防火墙上关闭 TCP 540 端口。若无需 UUCP 功能，建议直接卸载 uucp 软件包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0641","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0641.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0641","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0641.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0641.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0641.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5v9j-2mwh-j984/GHSA-5v9j-2mwh-j984.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0641.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0958.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0956","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0956.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0640","title":"Gopher 服务远程信息泄露漏洞","description":"Unix 系统中 Gopher 服务（默认端口 70）被启用时，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该协议的文件检索功能探测系统目录结构、访问敏感文件，或结合其他服务漏洞实施进一步渗透攻击。该漏洞影响所有运行 Gopher 服务的 Unix 系统，攻击难度低且无需用户交互，严重威胁信息安全。建议关闭不使用的 Gopher 服务以减少攻击面。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0640"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.513","remediation":"立即停止运行 Gopher 服务，并从服务管理器禁用开机自启。若业务无需使用 Gopher 协议，建议彻底卸载 gopherd 软件包；如有历史数据兼容需求，可在防火墙层面封禁 TCP 端口 70 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0640","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0640.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0640","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0640.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0640.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0640.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-84x2-992j-4cgr/GHSA-84x2-992j-4cgr.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0640.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0f3e5505-8487-4fbd-876c-46c388a9795c.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/7ae10c2036875bb5ef530e18322e7ca2477ed16c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0956.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0954","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0954.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0639","title":"Unix Chargen 服务反射放大拒绝服务漏洞","description":"chargen（字符生成）服务是一种过时的网络诊断协议，默认监听 TCP/UDP 19 端口，在接收到连接请求后会持续输出大量字符数据。攻击者可通过伪造源 IP 地址向目标系统的 UDP chargen 服务发送小数据包，利用服务放大响应流量实施分布式拒绝服务（DDoS）攻击。此外，该服务无需认证即可访问，可能导致信息泄露和服务滥用。该问题属于安全配置缺陷，影响 Unix/Linux 及部分 Windows 系统中默认启用 inetd 的版本。修复措施为在 inetd 配置中禁用 chargen 服务（注释掉 /etc/inetd.conf 中相关行）或使用防火墙阻止外部对 19 端口的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0639"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.383","remediation":"在 Unix/Linux 系统中，编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 文件，注释或删除 chargen 相关行（如 chargen stream tcp nowait root internal），然后重启 inetd 服务（`kill -HUP <inetd_pid>`）。在 Windows 系统中，通过「服务」管理器禁用 \"Simple TCP/IP Services\" 或 \"Character Generator\" 服务。该服务为过时诊断协议，无业务依赖时应彻底禁用，防止被用于 UDP/TCP 反射放大攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0639","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0639.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0639","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0639.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0954.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0948","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0948.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0636","title":"多厂商 Discard 服务安全配置漏洞","description":"Discard 服务（RFC 863，TCP/UDP 端口 9）是一种诊断网络服务，收到所有数据后直接丢弃而不做任何处理。该服务在生产环境中启用会无谓增加系统攻击面，攻击者可通过端口扫描发现该服务并确认主机存活，用于网络侦察；在 UDP 模式下，还可被用于反射放大 DDoS 攻击的流量放大链，导致目标网络带宽耗尽。此外，大量向该服务发送数据包可能造成服务器资源消耗。该漏洞无需认证、可远程利用，影响所有启用了 discard 服务的系统，应关闭该服务或通过防火墙限制访问。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0636"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.037","remediation":"在 Linux/Unix 中编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 注释 discard 相关行（stream 和 dgram）并重启 inetd 服务；systemd 系统执行 systemctl mask discard.socket 停止并屏蔽 discard socket。Windows 系统通过控制面板取消勾选\"简单 TCP/IP 服务\"或运行 dism /online /disable-feature /featurename:SimpleTCP 卸载。同时建议在防火墙上阻断 TCP 和 UDP 端口 9 的入站流量，并检查禁用 echo（端口 7）、chargen（端口 19）等类似高危服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0636","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0636","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0636.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/SHN_discard.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--78c74f51-06af-4c13-a78e-77284614fcad.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo